Steps for executing

1) WordCount
hadoop jar <jar path> WordCount.WordCount
Input Location : /input
Output Location :  /finalOutput

2) Coocurrence
hadoop jar <jar path> sample.StripesDriver
hadoop jar <jar path> sample.PairsDriver
Input Location : /input
Output Location : /output

3) KMeans:
hadoop jar <jar path> FollowersCountClustering.ClusterDriver
Input Location : /input
Output : /tempDir/<Folder with highest counter value>

4) Shortest Path
hadoop jar <jar path> ShortestPathCalculator.ShortestPathDriver
Input : /input
Output: /tempDir/<Folder with highest counter value>


Source Codes attached
1) Data generator : Classes to make the MR output suitable for visualization
2) Tweet Analyzer : Main classes for the MR jobs
3) Tweet Aggregator : For collecting tweet information.


NOTE : The output values from the result have been represented in the project report . The actual result files could not be shared due to size limitations.

